## Read Excel spreadsheets




::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
library(httr) ; library(readxl)
tmp <- tempfile(fileext = ".xlsx")
GET(url = "https://.xlsx", write_disk(tmp))
df <- read_xlsx(tmp, sheet = "Sheet 1")
```
